name: team.accessLogs
desc: This method is used to get the access logs for users on a team.

errors.paid_only: This is only available to paid teams.
errors.over_pagination_limit: It is not possible to request more than 1000 items per page or more than 100 pages.
errors.account_inactive: Authentication token is for a deleted user or team.
errors.user_is_bot: This method cannot be called by a bot user.
